= List Submissions

- Epic: Assignment Submission
- Actor: Student
- MVP: Yes
- BR: BR-SUB-4
- Description / Notes: View a list of own submissions for a course.
- As a: Student
- I want to: See my submissions
- So that: I can track my progress and grades.
- Trigger: The student visits the "Grades" or "Submissions" section.
- Pre-condition:
    - The student is logged in.
- Post-condition:
    - A list of the student's submissions is displayed with their grades and feedback.
- Solution (Step-by-Step):
  - Go to the course page.
  - Click on "Grades" or "My Submissions".
  - The list of submitted assignments is displayed.
